    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted because ASTM F1717 mandates a single standardized test condition and the COU is explicitly scoped to that condition; no extrapolation to other loading rates is claimed. E/uval acceptance criteria met for stiffness and yield force QoIs. Force at 40 mm displacement passes percent-difference criterion. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device submission.",
